snippet.title: Tenebris Pictura - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Tenebris Pictura, an all-new adventure by the creators of Megaton Rainfall, is coming to PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Steam and Epic on August 31.

Pre-order on Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/tenebris-pictura/9PJPFVNC4KPB
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2059300
Wishlist on Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/p/tenebris-pictura-76ffdf

You'll be plunged back to the Victorian era, playing the role of a paranormal investigator with psychic abilities who has landed in a misty, convoluted island, brimming with mystery. Solve mind-blowing puzzles and hunt ultra-terrestrial beings that appear to have escaped from a strange collection of paintings.
